{"tid":2035524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"增肥42磅極速收身　鄧月平晒5吋事業線晒新戀情","createTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T04:44:47.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"72b2385c6a2428abf5c857fc2192023ef0db0905","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5791_1812930905ecba67c06418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5791_1812930905ecba67c06418.jpg&h=3d730d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nF級身材出名火辣的鄧月平（Larine），去年拍攝陳果電影《墮胎師》演壞腦肥妹仔，兩個月內成功增肥42磅，搞到荷爾蒙失調阿媽擔心到為她爆喊，不過，22歲得天獨厚的她，原來火速收身變回索女，早前閉關抗疫，亦頻頻出關呼吸大自然空氣，日前更到郊外野餐，身穿低胸長裙的她，連放多張照片大晒5吋深長事業線，照片充滿美感，原來疑似係新男友操刀！"},{"pid":"dedd3b924705469071b7204a13f0c1a4ae56efa5","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5790_7714762925ecba679c0839.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5790_7714762925ecba679c0839.jpg&h=5ac9fece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14歲已經街頭表演的鄧月平，擁有F級導彈身材，出道又被指貌似藝人黃翠如，而得巨胸翠如美譽，深得大班宅男追捧的她，近年就經常在ViuTV節目內大騷火辣身材，澎湃身材相當吸睛，不過，去年鄧月平就接受挑戰，唔做女神為拍戲變肥妹仔亦在所不計，參予陳果《墮胎師》演出的她，要為電影增肥，為達效果每日食足七餐狂谷，更麻辣火鍋做早餐，兩個月成功由101磅增肥至143磅，更因為急增磅至荷爾蒙失調，試過停經四個月，為演出犧牲極大！"},{"pid":"bb84495c4dd68506d56e7fab229afdc7f44578d1","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">野餐晒男友視角</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，勝在22歲青春無敵，Larine好快就成功收身變回索女，即使早前因肺炎疫情閉關，都不時去行山放風大晒美好身材。日前她又放出兩張去郊外野餐照片，身穿花花裙的她好青春，更乘機大晒5吋深長事業線，女神晒深坑一啲都唔奇，不過她晒線之餘，還tag了一位男友人，疑似炫耀新戀情。"},{"pid":"eb9854654b3cf504b58237b2e2a3a5084ac95cd3","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5793_15310482335ecba6800c54d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5793_15310482335ecba6800c54d.jpg&h=b32a019a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而因肺炎疫情關係被迫停工的Larine本來要到澳洲及沖繩拍攝節目亦被迫延期，近日她就轉搞YouTube Channel及籌備ViuTV新劇，繼續搞作多多！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5792_6995341005ecba67dd5384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5792_6995341005ecba67dd5384.jpg&h=bd98febe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd92054cf593beb20f7444acfa647a2205fa456f","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5797_21067301225ecba675efb31-1024x1021.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5797_21067301225ecba675efb31-1024x1021.jpg&h=2ffda998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧月平做Gym亦不吝嗇晒堅挺巨胸好身材。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/img_5796_20257039145ecba67424bb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fimg_5796_20257039145ecba67424bb4.jpg&h=9ff55974&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"515ba27c5a38d752ab52f131e56e3aa01e5c0304","tid":2035524,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"見到墮胎師笑撚咗 套戲上咗未"},{"pid":"472f9d837ad95162b44129306b990edd199cb85b","tid":2035524,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/0